<seg id="1049">The recursive method starts with 4 rays of each pixel. if the difference between the colour values exceeds the default threshold, then the pixel is divided into 4 sub-pixels, which are followed individually and checked for further subdivisions. the maximum depth of the recursion can be set with the depth value.</seg>
